# CouplesConnection Server

## Compiling
- Install and configure Apache Ant (http://ant.apache.org/)
- Create a copy of template.build.xml called build.xml
- Install Apache Tomcat (http://tomcat.apache.org/) to a seperate location (tomcat_home)
- Update the catalina.home property in build.xml to point to the tomcat home directory
- Copy the contents on cc-server/lib to tomcat_home/lib
- Run <ant dist> to build dist/cc-server.war